<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="no-js">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title></title>

    <!-- DETECT JS -->
    <script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace("no-js","js");</script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Playfair+Display:700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    {# capture the CSS content as a Nunjucks variable #}
    {% set css %}
      {% include "css/main.css" %}
    {% endset %}

    {# feed it through our cssmin filter to minify #}
    <style>
      {{ css | cssmin | safe }}
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>

    <header class="[ o-wrapper ] [ site-header ]">
      <div>
        <h1 class="site-name"><span>Cardiff</span> Eats</h1>
        <p class="site-strapline">Local delivery information for Cardiff's restaurant and cafes during the <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/coronavirus-covid-19/">Coronavirus (COVID-19)</a> closures.</p>
      </div>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#vendor">Get your business on this list</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about">About this list</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="o-wrapper">
        {% block content %}
        {{ content | safe }}
        {% endblock %} 
      </div><!-- .o-wrapper -->
    </main>

    <aside class="o-wrapper">
      <h2 id="vendor">Get your business on this list</h2>
      <p>It would be great to support as many local businesses as we can through this challenging time. To be added to the list, email me &mdash; <a href="mailto:hello@matthewpassmore.co.uk">hello@matthewpassmore.co.uk</a> &mdash; with your opening hours and how people can order.</p>
      <h2 id="about">About this list</h2>
      <p>Thank you to <a href="https://twitter.com/ViningSarah">Sarah Vining</a> for the original idea and hard work collating this information. You can also <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1e7-a8KZ0Hg5PSihXrTV-LAjZdANwvqh2">download Sarah's lovely printable versions</a>.</p>
    </aside>

    <footer class="o-wrapper">
      <p class="rules"><strong>Stay at home. Wash your hands.</strong></p>
    </footer>

    <script>{% include 'js/main.js' %}</script>
  </body>
</html>
